description: ["The Danby DFF070B1BSLDB-6 medium sized refrigerator is the right fit for any apartment, office or condo. With its modern, smudge free stainless look and sleek hidden hinges, this mid sized fridge makes simple look stunning. Engineered with food storage in mind, the versatile interior provides the ultimate in controlled air flow without loss of space or storage capacity. 3 adjustable glass shelves, 1 clear vegetable crisper and 3 clear door shelves are brightly complimented with the white LED lighting. The frost free freezer section is the ultimate in easy maintenance. With no manual defrosting, there is no ice build up which means no freezer burnt food. Energy star certified, over energy consumption isn't a worry. Complete with a reversible door for left and right swing and integrated handle, this fridge is the perfect host for all your snacks, drinks and family favorites."]

description: ['Summit Appliance offers a quality line of built-in all-refrigerators specially designed for user-friendly operation in outdoor settings. Model SPR627OS is a 24â€ wide all-refrigerator that can be used built-in or freestanding in any outdoor location. It comes with a jet black cabinet and a user-reversible stainless steel door equipped with a pro style handle and front lock. The sealed back design and ground fault circuit interrupter offer added safety from the elements in the outdoors. Frost-free operation ensures minimum maintenance, with digital controls for easy temperature management. Adjustable glass shelves offer easy storage, with a slotted floor that can safely hold bottles in place. Additional features include LED lighting and a Sabbath mode setting. The flat door liner is great for fitting deeper trays inside. The SPR627OS can be used in household or commercial settings. It is ETL-S listed to NSF-7 commercial standards and ENERGY STARÂ® certified as a commercial refrigerator.']

description: ["The Danby Health pharmaceutical refrigerator combines innovative technology and proven reliability demanded by medical and clinical facilities. This medical refrigerator is the ideal option for storing temperature sensitive goods. Featuring an internal forced air fan and wire shelves, cool air is evenly distributed and remains consistent. In addition, the integrated temperature logger measures the internal temperature every 10 minutes and stores the readings. This data is saved in a. CSV file and can be extracted via USB at your convenience. Product safety is easily regulated with it's high/low alarm, sounding when the temperature rises or falls outside the set range. Lastly, with its LED lighting and hospital grade power cord, this unit offers an all around professional look and performance."]

This model offers 4.7 cu. ft. of cooling and freezing capacity and is Energy-Star compliant to help keep electricity costs as low as possible. It has a high-tech mechanical thermostat to make sure your foods are always stored at the correct temperature and has a handy cycle defrosting system. It comes with an intelligent reversible-door feature which allows you to adjust it for either left or right-handed opening. This glamorous fridge/freezer is a breeze to keep clean due to the stunning Black Stainless finish. Inside the appliance youâ€™ll find a bright interior light as well as a see-through vegetable crisper with glass cover and plenty of space for tall bottles. The integrated door handle adds another touch of class. This highly-efficient appliance also features an 12 month warranty on parts and labor.']

features_en: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR COMBO: 18 cubic ft. top mount freezer refrigerator with a pre-installed ice maker is ENERGY STAR certified and provides ample storage for fresh and frozen items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Adjustable split shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, while frost-free freezer prevents freezer burn', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items, while the utility bin offers easy-access to your favorite foods', 'KEEPS PRODUCE FRESH: 2 clear bottom plastic crisper drawers are humidity controlled for fresher and crispier fruits and vegetables, and slide out easily for removal of produce', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 29 7/8" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H with a 13.12 cubic ft. fresh food compartment and 5.07 cubic ft. freezer compartment for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, thereâ€™s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The convenient ice maker ensures your beverages stay cold, while the large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. No Remote Diagnostics', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: Features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items, as well as LED lighting for a warm, natural light', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: Adjustable, easy to remove shelving customizes your storage space, while gallon door bins provide space for taller and wider food or beverage items', 'LOW MAINTENANCE, HIGH PERFORMANCE: Clean back design hides condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better refrigerating performance and less maintenance', 'IDEAL SIZE: Measures 33.8" x 32.87" x 66.1" for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space in your home, office, or garage']
description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 21 cubic ft. of interior space and long-lasting LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features full-width adjustable glass shelves to suit your food storage needs and 2 clear plastic crisper drawers to keep fruits and vegetables fresh. It also features slide-out glass storage shelves for easy access and removal of pies, cakes, casseroles, and larger food items. With the refrigerator\'s convenient door storage, thereâ€™s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The gallon door bins make it easy to store tall items and beverages alongside your favorite sauces, condiments, and other ingredients. The tall item accommodation on the bottom shelf means more space for bottles of wine and water, while the convenient ice maker ensures your beverages stay cold out of the fridge as well. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized with two door bins and a single shelf. The 5.8 cubic ft. freezer also helps reduce freezer burn on your freezer and frozen food. The white refrigerator features a clean back design that hides the condenser coils, preventing the accumulation of dust and providing you with better performance. The ENERGY STAR certified fridge with energy efficient lighting meets EPA standards and can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator measures 33.8" x 32.87" x 66.1" for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

features_en: ['FREEZER AND REFRIGERATOR: 29.5 cu. ft. 4-door fridge and freezer provides ample fresh and frozen food storage and filters changed', 'CONVENIENT STORAGE: 20.16 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space for fresh foods and 8.93 cubic feet of freezer storage, and has 5 gallon-size door bins for taller and wider food or beverage items', 'EASY ACCESS SHELVING: 3 large flexible shelves offer customizable food storage and easy access and removal of casseroles and larger food items, and drawer style freezer holds all the frozen essentials', 'KEEPS FOODS FRESH: Triple Evaporator design creates separate cooling climates for the freezer, fridge, and ice compartments, while humidity controlled crispers ensure fresh fruits and veggies', 'ENERGY SAVING 4-DOOR REFRIGERATOR: French door refrigerator measures 35.87" W x 38.14" D x 68.82" H, and is ENERGY STAR certified']
description: ['The Kenmore 29.5 cu. ft. ENERGY STAR 4-Door Smart French Door Refrigerator offers plenty of fresh and frozen food storage, while providing your kitchen with a sleek and modern design. This fridge also features an Active Finish exterior ensuring it is easy to clean and fingerprint smudge resistant. With 20.16 cubic feet of interior refrigerated space and 8.93 cubic feet of freezer storage, you can stock up at the grocery store without running out of space. It also offers three large flexible shelves for customizable food storage that allows for easy access and removal of larger food and beverage items. Additional storage features, like five gallon-size door bins, allow you to store taller and wider food or beverage products. The drawer style freezer holds all of your frozen essentials, like pizzas, frozen meals, and ice cream. To keep foods fresh, the French door style fridge with freezer features a Triple Evaporator design that creates separate cooling climates for the freezer, refrigerator, and ice making compartments. The freezer has a dryer climate, while the fridge has a more humid climate. The humidity controlled crisper drawers keep your fruits and vegetables fresh, crisp, and delicious. This energy saving 4-door refrigerator/freezer combo features a French door style and measures 35.87" W x 38.14" D x 68.82" H, and is ENERGY STAR certified.']

description: ['When it comes to food storage, nothing comes close to the Kenmore Top Freezer and Refrigerator. This large top freezer refrigerator has 18 cubic ft. of interior space and energy efficient LED lighting, perfect for storing snacks, leftovers, lunches, and cans of soda in your home or office. The refrigerator features adjustable split shelves to suit your food storage needs and accommodate taller food and beverage containers like 2-liter bottles. The clear plastic crisper drawers keep fruits and vegetables fresh, while the utility bin provides easy access to your favorite foods. With the refrigerator\'s gallon-size door bins, thereâ€™s no more trying to figure out how to fit all the food inside. The large, easy-to-grip handles make opening and closing the doors a breeze. The frost-free top freezer helps you keep frozen food nice and organized and helps reduce freezer burn. The fridge can be placed in garages that get as cold as 39 degrees Fahrenheit with no additional adaptors and comes with a built-in ice maker to keep your beverages cool. Kenmore recommends measuring your space to ensure the freezer/refrigerator combo will fit. The Top-Freezer Refrigerator with a finger-print resistant stainless steel finish measures 29.76" W x 32.4" D x 66.57" H for the perfect amount of versatile food storage space.']

description: ["The Avanti can beverage cooler lets you store your favorite canned drinks at the perfect temperature with its adjustable temperature settings. Compact and stylish, this sleek black and stainless-steel beverage cooler is great for the home, office or small spaces like RVs and boats, or for supplementary drink storage in your kitchen. With 5.1 cubic feet of space, this beverage center can hold a total of 126 12 oz cans of your favorite beer or soda. You'll keep everyone happy by having plenty of their favorites chilled to perfection! This portable mini fridge boasts a durable and reversible double paned tempered glass door, which can easily be opened and closed on the side of your choosing and is the perfect mini fridge for the office, dorm, man cave, she shed, bar, bedroom, or anywhere you need a little extra refrigerator cooling and storage space. Easily see all your drinks through the glass door and use the adjustable, removable shelving for easy access to your favorite drinks. This compact fridge features automatic defrost, so your drinks stay consistently and perfectly chilled. Select the right setting at the touch of a button and monitor the temperature seamlessly with the LED electronic display. Designed for freestanding or built-in installation. Proper ventilation is required to maintain optimal cooling and overall performance. See instruction manual for proper installation."]

features_en: ['Make the best use of space by installing your refrigerator under the counter', 'Approved for use in the outdoors, with a sealed exterior and double pane tempered glass door', 'Heat resistant design provides clear view of stored products, with an elegant trim in seamless stainless steel', 'Ideal for home wet bars, island kitchens, and other applications with limited footprint space', 'Three glass shelves with six positions for optimal storage and easy cleaning']
description: ['The SPR489OS features a versatile design that meets NSF-7 and UL-471 commercial standards, but is also approved for residential use. Sized at just 19 inches wide and 17 inches deep, it features a jet black cabinet with a sealed back for safe installation in the outdoors. The user-reversible double pane tempered glass door includes a seamless stainless steel trim and a pro style handle. A factory installed lock offers added security, while the space-saving right angle plug and integrated hinge provide added flexibility in unit placement. Two leveling legs keep the unit level on uneven surfaces. Inside, the SPR489OS utilizes an internal fan to ensure the interior is evenly cooled from top to bottom. An automatic defrost system allows for minimal user maintenance, while the white interior and LED lighting allows full visibility of stored items. Three adjustable glass shelves with six positions provide optimal storage capacity inside the 3.1 cu. ft. interior. The dial thermostat, with seven temperature settings, is located in the upper-right corner for easy temperature management.']

features_en: ['44 WINE BOTTLE STORAGE CAPACITY - Enjoy this wine center with plenty of space to store all your favorite red and white wines, with three full-width and one half-width sliding wooden shelves', 'DUAL ZONE WINE FRIDGE - The dual zone beverage center has two independently controlled distinct zones that maintain temperatures between 41 and 61 F, keeping both red and white wines at the perfect serving temperature', 'TRIPLE PANE GLASS DOOR - The easy-to-clean triple pane glass door improves temperature stability, reduces condensation and enhances energy efficiency compared to a double pane glass door', 'CAPACITIVE TOUCH ELECTRONIC CONTROLS - Premium under glass controls provide quick and easy temperature adjustments to each zone', 'INTERIOR LED LIGHTING - This stylish wine cooler with recessed LED lights gradually increase in brightness as the door opens, making items easier to find']

Dual Zones keep red and white wine flowing at just the right temperature while the LED lighting ramps up when the door is open so you can see your way to the perfect pour. A striking edge-to-edge glass finish door creates an easy-to-clean, stylish look for your kitchen or bar area. The triple pane glass improves temperature stability, reduces condensation and enhances energy efficiency compared to a double pane glass door. Stylish controls let you select temperatures with just a touch, keeping the inside cool while the party heats up. Other features include an integrated handle perfect for tight spaces, easy-to-hear door alarm, a reversible door, independent power and lighting contols, and Sabbath-mode for Sabbath-observing practices.']
